extends ./layout.jade

block content
  section.header
    h1 Let's make something beautiful.
    p Choose from our packages we offer in both photo and video.
  section#investments.investments
    ul.investment
      h1 Photo
      li.investment__item Each package includes 2 shooters
      li.investment__item #[strong 4 hours • $1500]#[br]getting ready, portraits, ceremony, family photos, more portraits
      li.investment__item #[strong 6 hours • $2000]#[br]getting ready, portraits, ceremony, family photos, more portraits, light reception coverage
      li.investment__item #[strong 8 hours • $2500]#[br]getting ready, portraits, ceremony, family photos, more portraits, full reception coverage (w/o send-off)
      li.investment__item #[strong 10+ hours • $3000]#[br]getting ready, portraits, ceremony, family photos, more portraits, full reception coverage (with send-off)
    ul.investment
      h1 Video
      li.investment__item Each package includes 2 shooters
      li.investment__item #[strong 4 hours • 3-5 mins • $2000]#[br]getting ready, basic interview/message to partner, ceremony, bridal party &amp; couple shots
      li.investment__item #[strong 6 hours • 6-8 mins • $2500]#[br]getting ready, basic interview/message to partner, ceremony, bridal party &amp; couple shots, light reception coverage
      li.investment__item #[strong 8 hours • 8-10 mins • $3000]#[br]getting ready, basic interview/message to partner, ceremony, bridal party &amp; couple shots, full reception coverage (w/o send-off)
      li.investment__item #[strong 10+ hours • 12+ mins • $3500]#[br]getting ready, basic interview/message to partner, ceremony, bridal party &amp; couple shots, full reception coverage (with send-off)
    ul.addons
      h1 Photo add-ons
      li.addons__item #[strong $300 •] engagement session
      li.addons__item #[strong $250 •] rehearsal dinner
      li.addons__item #[strong $100/hr •] any extra events or happenings leading up to the big day
    ul.addons
      h1 Video add-ons
      li.addons__item #[strong $300 •] engagement session
      li.addons__item #[strong $250 •] rehearsal dinner
      li.addons__item #[strong $350 •] audio from the vows
      li.addons__item #[strong $100/hr •] any extra events or happenings leading up to the big day
    p.hesitate Do not hesitate to #[a(href="/contact") contact] us if you're worried about anything.#[<br />]We're in the business of telling stories, and we would love to get the chance to tell yours.
